{"nodes": [{"id": "docs_superpowers_specs_2026_07_08_afazeres_obra_design_afazeres_obra", "label": "Lista de afazeres dentro da obra", "file_type": "document", "source_file": "docs/superpowers/specs/2026-07-08-afazeres-obra-design.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "O pai quer anotar o que falta fazer/comprar ('pagar pedreiro', 'buscar tinta'), riscar e apagar. Checklist simples por obra \u2014 YAGNI expl\u00edcito: sem prazo, sem t\u00f3pico, sem virar gasto, sem badge. Painel fica entre A\u00e7\u00f5es e Gr\u00e1ficos: os 4 KPIs continuam no topo (regra 'saldo em 5s' \u2014 nada compete com eles)."}, {"id": "docs_superpowers_specs_2026_07_08_afazeres_obra_design_afazeres_checklist", "label": "Checklist afazeres por obra ({id, texto, feito})", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/superpowers/specs/2026-07-08-afazeres-obra-design.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Campo opcional afazeres:[] na obra; obras antigas usam o.afazeres || [] \u2014 sem migra\u00e7\u00e3o em empty()/normaliza(). Pendentes primeiro, feitos embaixo riscados. Apagar sem confirm: a\u00e7\u00e3o barata, pedido de 'rapidinho'. id via uid(), mesmo gerador dos gastos."}, {"id": "app_renderafazeres", "label": "renderAfazeres(o) (app.js)", "file_type": "code", "source_file": "docs/superpowers/specs/2026-07-08-afazeres-obra-design.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Monta o <ul> e liga os binds, chamada no fim de renderObra \u2014 mesmo padr\u00e3o de renderGastosFiltrados. CSS reusa panel/list/li-del; s\u00f3 uma classe .done."}, {"id": "docs_superpowers_specs_2026_07_08_afazeres_obra_design_re_resolucao_por_id", "label": "Padr\u00e3o: handlers re-resolvem obra/item por id (pegadinha do snapshot)", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "docs/superpowers/specs/2026-07-08-afazeres-obra-design.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "O snapshot da nuvem troca os objetos de db; handlers de clique re-resolvem a obra por id (obraById(obraAberta)) e o afazer por id na hora do clique \u2014 nunca guardam refer\u00eancia do render."}, {"id": "docs_superpowers_specs_2026_07_08_afazeres_obra_design_bump_do_service_worker", "label": "Bump do cache do Service Worker a cada release (obras-vN)", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "docs/superpowers/specs/2026-07-08-afazeres-obra-design.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Sem bump do nome do cache o celular instalado serve vers\u00e3o velha \u2014 li\u00e7\u00e3o do bug de cache. Aparece em todos os specs: obras-v6 (relat\u00f3rio simulador), v8 (iOS), v10 (tela gr\u00e1ficos), v13 (KPIs na obra), v15 (afazeres)."}], "edges": [{"source": "docs_superpowers_specs_2026_07_08_afazeres_obra_design_afazeres_obra", "target": "docs_superpowers_specs_2026_07_08_afazeres_obra_design_afazeres_checklist", "relation": "references", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "docs/superpowers/specs/2026-07-08-afazeres-obra-design.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "docs_superpowers_specs_2026_07_08_afazeres_obra_design_afazeres_obra", "target": "docs_superpowers_specs_2026_07_08_afazeres_obra_design_re_resolucao_por_id", "relation": "references", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "docs/superpowers/specs/2026-07-08-afazeres-obra-design.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "app_renderafazeres", "target": "docs_superpowers_specs_2026_07_08_afazeres_obra_design_afazeres_checklist", "relation": "implements", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "docs/superpowers/specs/2026-07-08-afazer